  "description": {
    "zh": "好了，下一批货单。更多的注射针剂。\n\n这次是更大的订单，我猜买家每次都会增加订单量，也许他只是在测试我们。总之，我依旧会给你发清单。\n\n记住一定要亲自找到它们，我们不要那些已经用过或者旧的东西，明白吗？",
    "en": "Alright, next shipment. More stimulants.\nIt's a bigger order this time, I am assuming this buyer will increase the order every time, maybe he is just testing us. Anyway, I am sending  you the list.\n\nMake sure you actually find them yourself, we don't want something that is being sold or used already, got it?"
  },
